Drunkard.Recipes.change_recipe(boilermaker) |> put_change(:steps, "Method 1: \"Bomb\".\n1. Pour 250ml beer into a beer glass.\n2. Drop a shot of whiskey into the beer, so that it stands at the bottom.\n3. Quickly drink the cocktail in one go.\nMethod 2: \"Chaser\".\n1. Serve a shot of whiskey and a glass of beer separately.\n2. Quickly drink the whiskey and \"chase\" it with a big sip of beer. Then finish the beer as usual.\nMethod 3. \"Upside down bomb\".\nIn Germany this method sometimes called \"U-Boot\" and may be made with vodka.\n1. Make a full shot of whiskey and hold it inside of an empty beer glass turned upside down, so that the bottom of the beer glass is tight against the top of the whiskey shot.\n2. Quickly flip everything over so that the whiskey shot is now upside down at the bottom of the beer glass.\n3. Fill the glass with beer. The whiskey will pour into the beer while you're drinking.\nMethod 4: Mix.\nSimply pour a shot of whisky into a pint of beer.") |> Repo.update!()
